com.rbmhtechnology.vind.annotations

Annotation Type Id


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Documented
public @interface Id
    The unique id of an item in the Search-Index. Values will be converted to a String-representation and optionally extended with prefix/suffix.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      Class<? extends IdGenerator> generator
      A generator to compose/decompose the ID value.
      String prefix
      A prefix that will be prepended to an ID value.
      String suffix
      A suffix that will be appended to an ID value

    • Element Detail

      • prefix

        public abstract String prefix
        A prefix that will be prepended to an ID value.
        Returns:
        String prefix to be prepended to the ID. By default empty.
        Default:
        ""

      • suffix

        public abstract String suffix
        A suffix that will be appended to an ID value
        Returns:
        String suffix to be appended to the ID. By default empty.
        Default:
        ""

      • generator

        public abstract Class<? extends IdGenerator> generator
        A generator to compose/decompose the ID value.
        Returns:
        IdGenerator class to automatically create the ids.
        Default:
        com.rbmhtechnology.vind.annotations.id.DefaultIdGenerator.class
